reviewText:
I'm from the fifties so I was used to stories and actor makeups. At least then they even tried their best to make an extraterrestrials look as such. The costumes and acting in this movie is so hokey and the (so called) story is so bad that I wish that there were some way I could get my money back.
  Advice to author of this movie! Get a grip and learn from those before you. Or at least watch some movies from that era. Better yet, make some trailers so people can see how stupid this movie is.
